<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='880164' id='t-880164'>But it begins with a journey that I myself have made,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='883326' id='t-883326'>asking hard questions of received wisdoms</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='886295' id='t-886295'>in sexual life.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='888103' id='t-888103'>And it is a journey which has
only served to strengthen my faith,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='892616' id='t-892616'>and my appreciation of local histories and cultures</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='896134' id='t-896134'>by showing me possibilities 
where I once only saw absolutes.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:12
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='901929' id='t-901929'>Now given the turmoil in many
countries in the Arab region,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='905386' id='t-905386'>talking about sex, 
challenging the taboos,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='908463' id='t-908463'>seeking alternatives might sound like
something of a luxury.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:24
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='913799' id='t-913799'>But at this critical moment in history,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='916591' id='t-916591'>if we do not anchor freedom and justice,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='920969' id='t-920969'>dignity and equality,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='922601' id='t-922601'>privacy and autonomy in our personal lives,
in our sexual lives,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='927843' id='t-927843'>we will find it very hard to achieve in public life.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:43
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='932144' id='t-932144'>The political and the sexual are intimate bedfellows,
and that is true for us all.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='938899' id='t-938899'>no matter where we live and love.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
15:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='942310' id='t-942310'>Thank you.</span>
</span>
</p>
